original: Bäckman, Gustaf August Natanael, stadskamrer, Amål, f. 26/5/90 i Bäck-seda, Jönköp. 1., av red. Aug. B. o. Augusta Lsakson. G. 23 m. Emy Som-mansson. Barn: Sven f. 25. — Sam-:sk. i Vetlanda, hand :.sk. där 16. Kom-m:kamrer i Vetlanda 12-18, istads-kamrer i Amål 18.
translated: Bäckman, Gustaf August Natanael, town treasurer, from Amål, born on May 26, 1890 in Bäck-seda, Jönköp. County, son of editor Aug. B. and Augusta Lsakson. Married on March 23, 19xx to Emy Som-mansson. They had a son named Sven, born in 1925. Worked as a clerk in Vetlanda and as a merchant in the same town for 16 years. Became the deputy treasurer in Vetlanda from 1912-1918 and then became the town treasurer in Amål from 1918 onward.
